<P>__{(starts a bagpipe record of "scotland the brave")}
<D>__{dance with me. one, two, one two three four. one, two, one two three four. "for the second time..." one two three four "... in the lives of most of us..." one, two, one two three four "... we are at war." three, four.}
<A>__{dancing at arm's length with logue, bertie repeats:}
